component_description: Detection results for Header Progress Bar

elements.label: Header Progress Bar > Status Indicator
elements.description: Yellow horizontal progress bar at the top of the screen, positioned directly under the phone status bar
elements.explanation: Box tightly fits the yellow progress bar horizontally and vertically, with only 1-2 pixel excess at the left. Good alignment overall.

elements.label: Header Progress Bar > Back Button
elements.description: Gray left-pointing arrow icon positioned at the left side of the header area, below the status bar
elements.explanation: Box closely fits the gray back arrow icon. Minimal space around the icon; accurate size and placement for the described element.

elements.label: Continue Button > Button
elements.description: Large green rectangular button with rounded corners and white text 'CONTINUE' at the bottom of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the visible button's position and size, with only a minor excess on the right edge. No correction necessary.

elements.label: Reminder Prompt > Title
elements.description: Bold gray text 'Get a daily reminder to meet your goal' centered in the upper portion of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely fits the title text, with minimal padding above and below. Very accurate.

elements.label: Reminder Prompt > Duolingo Mascot
elements.description: Green cartoon owl character holding a yellow bell, positioned in the middle section of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box accurately covers the owl mascot and bell, with a slight omission of the owl's left wing, but otherwise fits well.

elements.label: Reminder Prompt > Speech Bubble
elements.description: White speech bubble with text 'Just in case you forget!' next to the green owl character
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly fits the speech bubble and the text, closely matching the element's shape and placement.

component_description: Detection results for Notification Permission Card

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Container
elements.description: White rectangular card with rounded corners containing the notification permission request, positioned in the middle of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box very closely follows the card's edges with minimal excess gutter, only a couple of pixels extra at bottom and sides.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > App Icon
elements.description: Small green square icon with cartoon eyes, positioned at the left side within the notification card
elements.explanation: Box tightly frames the app icon, matching the element position and size; extra margin is minimal.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Message
elements.description: Text stating 'The website "duolingo.com" would like to send you notifications in Notification Center.' centered in the card
elements.explanation: Box accurately covers the full message text, with minor horizontal extension to the left not affecting inclusion.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Helper Text
elements.description: Small gray text 'Notifications can be changed in Safari Website preferences.' at the bottom of the notification card
elements.explanation: Annotated box is much wider than the actual helper text and too tall. Suggested box more tightly encloses the visible helper line.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Block Button
elements.description: Gray rectangular button with text 'BLOCK' on the lower left side of the notification card
elements.explanation: Box closely frames the 'BLOCK' button; both vertical and horizontal fit are correct, with only slight overreach.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Allow Button
elements.description: Blue rectangular button with white text 'ALLOW' on the lower right side of the notification card
elements.explanation: Box covers the 'ALLOW' button well, closely matching the actual UI element's boundaries.

elements.label: Notification Permission Card > Direction Indicator
elements.description: Light blue upward-pointing arrow below the notification card
elements.explanation: Box frames the blue arrow with only minimal, visually negligible padding.
